headline: Here's Why Some Investors Have Growing Expectations for Starbucks Stock Right Now
summary: Investors recognize that Starbucks needs a turnaround and some believe that it's an easy bar to jump over.  Starbucks is looking to improve the customer experience and there are signs that it's headed in the right direction.  Returns for Starbucks (NASDAQ: SBUX) stock are completely flat over the last five years, as of this writing, but some investors believe better days are ahead.
